46\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 18}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?dos arvadeus, dos zemareus e dos hamateus. Depois as fam\u237?lias dos cananeus se espalharam. }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 19}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Assim, o territ\u243?rio dos cananeus se estendia de S\u237?don at\u233? Gerar, perto de Gaza, at\u233? Sodoma, Gomorra, Adm\u225? e Zeboim, perto de Lasa. }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 20}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Esses foram os filhos de C\u227? segundo suas fam\u237?lias e suas l\u237?nguas, conforme suas terras e suas na\u231?\u245?es.\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 21}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Sem, antepassado de todos os filhos de \u201?ber e irm\u227?o de\u160?Jaf\u233?, o mais velho,}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11  tamb\u233?m teve filhos. }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 22}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Os filhos de Sem foram El\u227?o, Assur, Arpaxade, Lude e Ar\u227?.\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 23}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Os filhos de Ar\u227? foram Uz, Hul, G\u233?ter e M\u225?s.\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 24}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\lan